secubox-device-intel (1.1.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Add OpenWRT/SecuBox device detection
  * MAC vendor fingerprinting for router manufacturers
  * HTTP probe for LuCI interface detection
  * DHCP hostname pattern matching (openwrt, lede, gl-, etc.)
  * mDNS/Avahi service discovery
  * New endpoints: /probe/openwrt, /openwrt, /mdns
  * Device tagging: is_router, router_vendor, is_openwrt, is_secubox

